title: AIIMS Kalyani Notification 2026 - Apply Online for Project Technical Support II Posts
description: All India Institute of Medical Sciences (AIIMS Kalyani) has declared the official notification for 2026. To fill up the vacancies for Project Technical Support II Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the Intermediate (10+2), DMLT, and Diploma can grab this chance and apply for the AIIMS Kalyani Notification 2026 . Here we mentioned more about the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts. Interested candidates ...
